00:01:26.787 --> 00:01:27.506
Not back yet.

00:01:27.707 --> 00:01:28.420
This...

00:01:29.666 --> 00:01:31.187
What should I do?

00:01:31.547 --> 00:01:32.786
Has something happened?

00:01:32.946 --> 00:01:33.632
Well.

00:01:34.106 --> 00:01:35.882
Miss Shen is in prison.

00:01:36.627 --> 00:01:37.807
So what?

00:01:37.987 --> 00:01:39.626
I passed by it just now.

00:01:40.226 --> 00:01:41.467
I heard

00:01:42.067 --> 00:01:43.986
