His Highness's reputation.

00:01:46.186 --> 00:01:47.266
If word gets out...

00:01:47.627 --> 00:01:48.357
Lead the way.

00:01:49.026 --> 00:01:50.536
His Highness cares deeply for her,

00:01:50.537 --> 00:01:51.382
yet she...

00:01:52.262 --> 00:01:52.945
Your Ladyship.

00:01:52.946 --> 00:01:53.945
Is that true?

00:01:53.946 --> 00:01:56.027
I only did it to protect
His Highness's reputation.

00:01:56.186 --> 00:01:57.506
If it weren't urgent,

00:01:57.507 --> 00:01:59.066
I wouldn't have disturbed you.

00:02:01.026 --> 00:02:02.187
There's no time.

00:02:04.026 --> 00:02:05.187
(Shen Qingru.)

00:02:05.826 --> 00:02:08.170
(Let's see how you explain this time.)

00:02:10.106 --> 00:02:10.982
Open the door!

00:02:17.867 --> 00:02:19.747
She really is a shameless woman.

00:02:20.707 --> 00:02:21.295
Your...

00:02:21.867 --> 00:02:22.626
Your Highness.

00:02:24.186 --> 00:02:25.066
Your Highness.

00:02:27.586 --> 00:02:28.786
How could it be you?

00:02:34.506 --> 00:02:35.626
Don't come near.

00:02:36.026 --> 00:02:36.867
Ru.

00:02:38.066 --> 00:02:38.745
Little beauty.

00:02:38.746 --> 00:02:39.626
Stay away!

00:02:45.506 --> 00:02:46.626
Don't come near!

00:02:48.827 --> 00:02:50.467
If you dare touch her,

00:02:52.346 --> 00:02:54.386
I'll make sure you die without a trace.

00:03:29.586 --> 00:03:30.547
Ru.

00:04:05.987 --> 00:04:07.187
Yuwen Que.

00:04:08.746 --> 00:04:10.587
You ruined me completely.

00:04:11.506 --> 00:04:13.506
Are you satisfied now?

00:04:16.387 --> 00:04:18.386
Go ahead, laugh at me all you want.

00:04:30.987 --> 00:04:31.946
It's been three years.

00:04:34.107 --> 00:04:35.787
Do you really hate me that much?

00:04:35.987 --> 00:04:36.946
Hate?

00:04:38.386 --> 00:04:41.227
You destroyed my whole family,
leaving us without a grave.

00:04:41.746 --> 00:04:44.266
No single word of hate can fix this.

00:04:44.987 --> 00:04:46.745
I wish you were dead.

00:04:46.746 --> 00:04:48.586
I've sent Heng Dao to investigate.

00:04:48.946 --> 00:04:49.906
Shut up.

00:04:49.907 --> 00:04:51.427
You executioner.

00:04:52.547 --> 00:04:53.547
Guards!

00:04:54.027 --> 00:04:54.747
Save...

00:04:55.667 --> 00:04:56.907
If you try to die,

00:04:57.706 --> 00:04:59.866
I'll make everyone you care
about die with you.

00:04:59.867 --> 00:05:01.146
You dare?

00:05:01.746 --> 00:05:02.987
We've known each other for years.

00:05:04.506 --> 00:05:05.706
You still don't know

00:05:06.107 --> 00:05:07.586
that I mean what I say.

00:05:13.787 --> 00:05:14.626
Open the door!

00:05:20.626 --> 00:05:21.867
How could it be you?

00:05:22.706 --> 00:05:24.107
You really think

00:05:26.027 --> 00:05:28.146
I don't know your tricks?

00:05:30.266 --> 00:05:31.946
I don't know what you're talking about.

00:05:32.706 --> 00:05:34.227
You drugged her.

00:05:35.427 --> 00:05:37.347
You had people ruin her reputation.

00:05:38.266 --> 00:05:39.307
All of it,

00:05:40.386 --> 00:05:41.987
you thought I didn't know?

00:05:42.306 --> 00:05:43.106
Your Highness.

00:05:43.107 --> 00:05:43.786
I...

00:05:43.787 --> 00:05:45.505
I only did it for you.

00:05:45.506 --> 00:05:47.182
I just wanted to protect you, I...

00:05:51.107 --> 00:05:52.227
Cousin.

00:05:52.667 --> 00:05:54.826
I truly didn't mean it.

00:05:54.907 --> 00:05:55.670
Your Highness.

00:05:55.946 --> 00:05:58.347
Before she passed, the Old Madam
entrusted the princess to you.

00:05:58.907 --> 00:06:01.227
She's your last family in this world.

00:06:04.186 --> 00:06:06.066
I searched for her

00:06:07.706 --> 00:06:09.227
across mountains and rivers,

00:06:10.506 --> 00:06:12.227
neglecting sleep and food.

00:06:12.467 --> 00:06:14.347
Finally, after so much effort...

00:06:18.266 --> 00:06:20.586
If I hear you speak one more word,

00:06:21.826 --> 00:06:24.227
I'll send you to meet your mother.

00:06:27.946 --> 00:06:29.466
I didn't see anything.

00:06:30.427 --> 00:06:32.107
I didn't hear anything.

00:06:32.826 --> 00:06:33.826
Get out!

00:06:52.787 --> 00:06:53.506
Your Highness.

00:06:53.547 --> 00:06:54.586
I take my leave.

00:07:08.787 --> 00:07:09.787
(Yuwen Que.)

00:07:10.706 --> 00:07:12.626
(You set up this prison for me.)

00:07:13.027 --> 00:07:15.506
(But you didn't know
I have my own spies inside.)

00:07:16.706 --> 00:07:17.626
(Ji.)

00:07:18.306 --> 00:07:19.826
(Wait for my signal.)

00:07:20.907 --> 00:07:22.670
(I must escape.)

00:07:42.107 --> 00:07:43.532
Shen Qingru.

00:07:43.667 --> 00:07:46.145
You're getting bolder by the day.

00:07:46.146 --> 00:07:47.466
In just a few days,

00:07:47.547 --> 00:07:49.226
you dare come to me,

00:07:49.227 --> 00:07:51.026
to secretly meet in this dungeon.

00:07:52.667 --> 00:07:54.747
How many guards have
you brought, Your Ladyship?

00:07:55.946 --> 00:07:57.385
Do you want to search me?

00:07:57.386 --> 00:07:58.227
You...

00:07:59.027 --> 00:08:00.026
Look.

00:08:01.746 --> 00:08:03.506
I don't even have a hairpin on me.

00:08:03.946 --> 00:08:06.626
Why be so guarded, Your Ladyship?

00:08:07.027 --> 00:08:08.466
Stop acting pitiful.

00:08:08.506 --> 00:08:10.346
Wasn't the last lesson enough?

00:08:10.347 --> 00:08:11.626
Lesson?

00:08:13.386 --> 00:08:15.427
I know Your Ladyship

00:08:16.146 --> 00:08:18.187
wants to kill me.

00:08:19.587 --> 00:08:20.946
But sadly...

00:08:21.386 --> 00:08:22.706
Sadly what?

00:08:23.266 --> 00:08:25.747
Sadly, you don't even
have the courage to kill me.

00:08:28.347 --> 00:08:30.066
You dare humiliate me?

00:08:31.266 --> 00:08:32.987
I'm just speaking the truth.

00:08:34.227 --> 00:08:35.667
You hate me, Your Ladyship.

00:08:36.027 --> 00:08:37.187
But you fear him.

00:08:38.162 --> 00:08:40.045
Caught between the two,

00:08:40.867 --> 00:08:42.306
does it trouble you?

00:08:42.307 --> 00:08:44.049
What exactly are you trying to say?

00:08:44.050 --> 00:08:45.326
Your Ladyship.

00:08:45.467 --> 00:08:46.826
How about I help you come up with

00:08:46.827 --> 00:08:48.787
a solution that satisfies both sides?

00:08:52.506 --> 00:08:53.547
What solution?

00:08:57.307 --> 00:08:59.066
Help me deliver a message.

00:08:59.266 --> 00:09:00.226
I promise

00:09:00.307 --> 00:09:02.025
I will disappear forever

00:09:02.026 --> 00:09:03.267
from both your lives.

00:09:04.227 --> 00:09:05.267
Deliver it to whom?

00:09:07.587 --> 00:09:10.147
Su Changji.

00:09:11.107 --> 00:09:14.357
This name should be familiar
to Your Ladyship.

00:09:15.786 --> 00:09:17.145
What do you want to do?

00:09:18.266 --> 00:09:19.782
I'm just

00:09:19.827 --> 00:09:22.307
a fish on a chopping board,
waiting to be cut.

00:09:23.426 --> 00:09:24.547
What can I do?

00:09:25.827 --> 00:09:28.346
Rather than being slowly tortured
to death by Yuwen Que,

00:09:28.587 --> 00:09:31.907
I might as well go all in.

00:09:34.386 --> 00:09:35.746
Your Ladyship, I beg you.

00:09:35.827 --> 00:09:37.346
Please help me this once.

00:09:37.347 --> 00:09:39.667
I swear, if you help me,

00:09:39.786 --> 00:09:41.667
I will immediately leave the capital.

00:09:42.067 --> 00:09:44.787
You and His Highness
can be together in harmony.

00:09:48.266 --> 00:09:49.667
Rare indeed,

00:09:50.067 --> 00:09:51.907
