00:09:52.266 --> 00:09:53.627
I'm just

00:09:54.546 --> 00:09:55.547
tired.

00:09:59.587 --> 00:10:00.547
Speak.

00:10:01.426 --> 00:10:02.826
What do you want me to deliver?

00:10:08.712 --> 00:10:10.272
Deliver this letter.

