When the old general fell in battle,

00:10:34.467 --> 00:10:36.505
you were never so despondent.

00:10:36.506 --> 00:10:37.507
Commander.

00:10:47.587 --> 00:10:49.826
(Do you want the military seal
or your life?)

00:10:49.827 --> 00:10:51.507
(Think carefully, General.)

00:10:51.746 --> 00:10:53.427
I give you three days, General.

00:10:59.626 --> 00:11:01.466
Ancestors of the Su family above,

00:11:01.906 --> 00:11:03.346
