00:11:19.386 --> 00:11:20.667
I know my guilt.

00:11:28.746 --> 00:11:29.986
From now on,

00:11:31.266 --> 00:11:32.706
I seek no fame or achievement.

00:11:33.546 --> 00:11:35.106
No desire to be recorded in history.

00:11:36.746 --> 00:11:37.466
I only...

00:11:40.587 --> 00:11:41.826
